In this project, I explored NLP Cloud to understand how Large Language Models (LLMs) and APIs work in real-world applications.
I implemented a console-based Login & Register system (without using any GUI) to strengthen my understanding of backend logic, API handling, and authentication flow.

This project focuses on:

Learning how LLM-powered services can be integrated using APIs

Understanding model selection and usage in NLP Cloud

Building a menu-driven authentication system using Python

Applying Object-Oriented Programming (OOP) concepts in a real project


